<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OPSC/UPSC Secure Examination Portal</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS for styling -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- CryptoJS for secure AES encryption -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/crypto-js/4.1.1/crypto-js.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Canvas Confetti for celebration effects -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.6.0/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
    
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            user-select: none; /* Prevent text selection */
        }
        .hidden-screen { display: none !important; }
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        }
        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f5f9; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #94a3b8; }
        
        #video-preview { transform: scaleX(-1); } /* Mirror webcam */
        
        /* Anti-cheat overlay animation */
        @keyframes pulse-red {
            0% { background-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.95); }
            50% { background-color: rgba(185, 28, 28, 0.95); }
            100% { background-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.95); }
        }
        .cheat-warning-bg { animation: pulse-red 2s infinite; }

        .glow-success {
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.6);
            border-color: #22c55e !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 h-screen w-screen overflow-hidden" oncontextmenu="return false;">

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 1: PORTAL SELECTION ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-selection" class="h-full w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-900 text-white relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')]"></div>
        <div class="z-10 text-center max-w-2xl px-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">OPSC / UPSC Secure Portal</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-300 mb-12 text-lg">Select your role to proceed into the examination environment.</p>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <button onclick="switchScreen('screen-setup')" class="group relative p-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all text-left overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-blue-500 transform scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 transition-transform origin-top"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-400">Aspirant Portal</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Take the proctored examination. Requires webcam and fullscreen permissions.</p>
                </button>
                
                <button onclick="switchScreen('screen-examiner-login')" class="group relative p-8 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 hover:border-emerald-500 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all text-left overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-2 h-full bg-emerald-500 transform scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 transition-transform origin-top"></div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-emerald-400">Examiner Dashboard</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Upload encrypted candidate files (.enc) to evaluate performance and proctor logs.</p>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 2: ASPIRANT SETUP ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-setup" class="hidden-screen h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-100 p-6">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-4xl w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">System Check & Setup</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 text-sm">Please verify your identity and accept the strict proctoring rules.</p>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" id="aspirant-name" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:outline-none" placeholder="Enter your full name">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Strict Anti-Cheat Rules:</h3>
                    <ul class="text-xs text-amber-700 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4">
                        <li>The exam runs in strict Fullscreen mode.</li>
                        <li>Tab switching or minimizing will be logged as violations.</li>
                        <li>Your webcam will take random snapshots during the exam.</li>
                        <li>Copy/Paste and Right-Click are disabled.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <button id="btn-start-exam" onclick="startExam()" class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 transition-all opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed" disabled>
                    Enable Camera to Start Exam
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative min-h-[300px]">
                <video id="video-preview" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" autoplay muted playsinline></video>
                <div id="camera-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-slate-900/80 z-10">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-400 mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                    <button onclick="initCamera()" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white text-sm rounded-lg transition-colors">Grant Camera Permission</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 3: EXAM INTERFACE ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-exam" class="hidden-screen h-full w-full flex flex-col bg-slate-50">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header class="h-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0 shadow-sm z-20">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                <span class="font-semibold text-slate-700 text-sm">Proctoring Active</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-xl font-mono font-bold text-slate-800 bg-slate-100 px-4 py-1 rounded-md border border-slate-200" id="timer-display">
                03:30:00
            </div>
            <button onclick="confirmSubmission()" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors text-sm">
                Submit Exam
            </button>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Layout -->
        <div class="flex flex-1 overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Sidebar (Modules) -->
            <aside class="w-64 bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 flex flex-col shrink-0">
                <div class="p-4 border-b border-slate-700">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1">Candidate</h3>
                    <p id="display-cand-name" class="font-medium text-white truncate">-</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-3">Modules</h3>
                    <ul id="module-tabs" class="space-y-1">
                        <!-- Populated dynamically -->
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <!-- Question Area -->
            <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8 relative">
                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pb-24" id="questions-container">
                    <!-- Populated dynamically -->
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ANTI-CHEAT OVERLAY -->
    <div id="fullscreen-warning" class="hidden-screen fixed inset-0 z-50 cheat-warning-bg flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-lg shadow-2xl">
            <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-red-600 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path></svg>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Proctoring Violation</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">You have exited fullscreen or switched tabs. This action has been logged. Continuous violations will result in disqualification.</p>
            <button onclick="returnToExam()" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg w-full">
                Return to Fullscreen & Resume
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 4: POST-EXAM RESULT & ENCRYPTION ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-result" class="hidden-screen h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-900 p-6 relative">
        <div id="result-card" class="glass-panel max-w-md w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8 text-center z-10 transition-all duration-1000">
            <div id="result-icon" class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
                <!-- Dynamic Icon -->
            </div>
            <h2 id="result-title" class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Exam Submitted</h2>
            <p id="result-message" class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Your responses have been recorded.</p>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-8">
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider mb-1">Preliminary Score</p>
                <p id="result-score" class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800">--%</p>
            </div>

            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4 text-left bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded border border-blue-100">
                <strong class="text-blue-700">Next Step:</strong> Download your encrypted exam file below and send it to your Examiner. Do not alter the file name.
            </p>
            
            <button onclick="downloadEncryptedFile()" class="w-full bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
                Download .enc File
            </button>
            <button onclick="location.reload()" class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 underline">Return to Home</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 5: EXAMINER LOGIN ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-examiner-login" class="hidden-screen h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center bg-slate-100 p-6">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-md w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
            <button onclick="switchScreen('screen-selection')" class="text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-1">
                &larr; Back
            </button>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6">Examiner Login</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-5">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1">Upload Aspirant File (.enc)</label>
                    <input type="file" id="upload-enc" accept=".enc" class="w-full text-sm text-slate-500 file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded-full file:border-0 file:text-sm file:font-semibold file:bg-emerald-50 file:text-emerald-700 hover:file:bg-emerald-100 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg p-2">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-1">Decryption Password</label>
                    <input type="password" id="eval-password" class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:outline-none" placeholder="Enter Examiner Password">
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">Default is: OPSC2026</p>
                </div>
                <button onclick="processExaminerFile()" class="w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                    Decrypt & Evaluate
                </button>
            </div>
            <p id="login-error" class="text-red-500 text-sm mt-4 text-center hidden-screen">Invalid password or corrupted file.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ==================== SCREEN 6: EXAMINER DASHBOARD ==================== -->
    <div id="screen-examiner-dashboard" class="hidden-screen h-full w-full flex flex-col bg-slate-50 overflow-hidden">
        <header class="h-16 bg-emerald-800 text-white flex items-center justify-between px-6 shrink-0 shadow-md z-20">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <button onclick="location.reload()" class="hover:text-emerald-300">&larr; Exit</button>
                <h1 class="font-bold text-lg">Evaluation Dashboard</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm font-medium bg-emerald-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-emerald-700" id="dash-candidate-name">
                Aspirant Name
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-6 md:p-8">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-8">
                
                <!-- Top Stats -->
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
                        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Total Score</p>
                        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800" id="dash-score">0/0</p>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium mt-1" id="dash-percentage">0%</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6 md:col-span-3">
                        <h3 class="text-slate-700 font-bold mb-4 border-b pb-2">Sectional Analysis</h3>
                        <div id="dash-section-bars" class="space-y-3">
                            <!-- Bars populated dynamically -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <!-- Analytics: Strengths & Weaknesses -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
                            Performance Diagnostics
                        </h3>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-emerald-100">
                                <h4 class="text-emerald-800 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Strong Modules (&ge;80%)</h4>
                                <ul id="dash-strong" class="text-sm text-emerald-700 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4"></ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-red-100">
                                <h4 class="text-red-800 font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Weak Modules (&lt;80%)</h4>
                                <ul id="dash-weak" class="text-sm text-red-700 space-y-1 list-disc pl-4"></ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-amber-200">
                            <h4 class="text-amber-800 font-bold text-sm mb-2">Examiner AI Recommendation for Next Phase:</h4>
                            <p id="dash-focus" class="text-sm text-amber-900 leading-relaxed"></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Proctoring Logs & Images -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path></svg>
                            Proctoring & Anti-Cheat Logs
                        </h3>
                        <div class="mb-6">
                            <h4 class="text-slate-600 font-semibold text-xs uppercase mb-2">Violation Log</h4>
                            <div id="dash-logs" class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded p-3 h-32 overflow-y-auto text-xs font-mono text-slate-700 space-y-1">
                                <!-- Logs -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-slate-600 font-semibold text-xs uppercase mb-2">Captured Identity Snapshots</h4>
                            <div id="dash-images" class="flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-2">
                                <!-- Base64 Images -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Detailed Answer Evaluation -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-slate-800 font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 border-b pb-3">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
                        Detailed Answer Evaluation
                    </h3>
                    <div id="dash-evaluation" class="space-y-6">
                        <!-- Questions mapped here -->
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hidden Canvas for capturing WebCam snapshots -->
    <canvas id="snapshot-canvas" class="hidden-screen"></canvas>

    <script>
        // =========================================================================
        // DATA LAYER: QUESTIONS DATABASE (Sample subset provided, add the rest here)
        // =========================================================================
        const examData = {
            modules: ["Indian Polity", "Indian Geography", "Indian History", "Quantitative Aptitude", "Logical Reasoning"],
            questions: [
{
        id: 1,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Consider the following statements regarding the Fundamental Rights guaranteed under Article 19 of the Indian Constitution:\n1. The right to freedom of speech and expression includes the freedom of commercial advertisements.\n2. The state can impose reasonable restrictions on the exercise of the right to assemble peaceably on the grounds of public order, sovereignty, and integrity of India, and morality.\n3. The right to reside and settle in any part of the territory of India is available to both citizens and foreigners.\nWhich of the statements given above is/are correct?",
        options: ["1 only", "1 and 2 only", "2 and 3 only", "1, 2, and 3"],
        correctIndex: 0,
        explanation: "Trap: Freedom of movement/residence is for citizens only, not foreigners. Assembly must be 'unarmed' as well."
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Assertion (A): The Supreme Court of India has exclusive original jurisdiction in any dispute between the Government of India and one or more States.\nReason (R): The original jurisdiction of the Supreme Court extends to any dispute arising out of any treaty, agreement, covenant, or engagement executed before the commencement of the Constitution.",
        options: ["Both A and R are true and R is the correct explanation of A.", "Both A and R are true but R is NOT the correct explanation of A.", "A is true but R is false.", "A is false but R is true."],
        correctIndex: 2,
        explanation: "Trap: Pre-constitution treaties are specifically excluded from original jurisdiction under Art 131."
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Match List-I (Parliamentary Committees) with List-II (Functions/Composition) and select the correct answer using the code given below:\nList-I\nA. Public Accounts Committee\nB. Estimates Committee\nC. Committee on Public Undertakings\nD. Rules Committee\nList-II\n1. Has 30 members, all from Lok Sabha.\n2. Examines the reports of the Comptroller and Auditor General (CAG).\n3. Considers matters of procedure and conduct of business in the House.\n4. Examines the reports and accounts of PSUs.",
        options: ["A-2, B-1, C-4, D-3", "A-1, B-2, C-4, D-3", "A-2, B-1, C-3, D-4", "A-4, B-1, C-2, D-3"],
        correctIndex: 0,
        explanation: "Fact: Estimates committee has 30 members, all from LS."
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Consider the following statements regarding the passing of Bills in the Indian Parliament:\n1. A Money Bill cannot be introduced in the Rajya Sabha, and the Rajya Sabha has a maximum of 14 days to return it with or without recommendations.\n2. In case of a deadlock over an Ordinary Bill, the President can summon a joint sitting, which is presided over by the Chairman of the Rajya Sabha.\n3. A Constitution Amendment Bill requires prior recommendation of the President before introduction.\nWhich of the statements given above is/are correct?",
        options: ["1 only", "1 and 2 only", "2 and 3 only", "1, 2, and 3"],
        correctIndex: 0,
        explanation: "Trap: Joint sitting is presided over by the Speaker of LS, not Chairman of RS; Constitutional Amendment Bills do not require prior Presidential recommendation."
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Consider the following statements regarding the Panchayati Raj Institutions (PRIs) under the 73rd Constitutional Amendment Act:\n1. It is mandatory for states to provide 50% reservation for women in Panchayats at all three levels.\n2. The State Election Commission, which conducts Panchayat elections, is appointed by the Governor but can only be removed in a manner similar to a judge of a High Court.\n3. The minimum age to contest Panchayat elections is 25 years.\nWhich of the statements given above is/are correct?",
        options: ["2 only", "1 and 2 only", "2 and 3 only", "1 and 3 only"],
        correctIndex: 0,
        explanation: "Trap: Reservation for women is 33%, not 50% mandated by 73rd CAA; minimum age is 21 years, not 25."
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        module: "Indian Polity",
        text: "Assertion (A): The scope of the writ jurisdiction of a High Court under Article 226 is wider than that of the Supreme Court under Article 32.\nReason (R): The Supreme Court can issue writs only for the enforcement of Fundamental Rights, whereas a High Court can issue writs for Fundamental Rights as well as for any other purpose.",
        options: ["Both A and R are true and R is the correct explanation of A.", "Both A and R are true but R is NOT the correct explanation of A.", "A is true but R is false.", "A is false but R is true."],
        correctIndex: 0,
        explanation: "Conceptual clarity. High courts cover legal rights beyond just fundamental rights."
    },
    {
        id: 7,
